  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0ddd \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf \u0d85\u0db0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dba \u0daf\u0dac\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db8\u0dca \u0daf\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "People's Court will punish if they become political gamblers",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Opposition Leader Sajith Premadasa said today (27) in the Parliament that if they jump around like political Gembo, they will have to respond to them before the People's Court.",
        "The leader of the opposition said this while joining the debate on the adoption of the emergency law in the parliament.",
        "The opposition leader said that today the government is talking about \"emergency\" but the people have an emergency of living without any essential goods and the government has an emergency of spreading state terrorism.",
        "The Leader of the Opposition said that the dream of the President as well as the Leader of the Prime Minister came true, but the dreams of 220 lakh people have been crushed."
      ],
